/image_1445810162.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742934-earnings-will-carry-s-and-p-500-higher-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 08:02:20"}, {"id": "4742933", "title": "Federal Signal Corporation: Upward Potential Not Reached Yet", "description": "<p class=\"p p1 editors-note-first-article\"><i><b>Editor's note:</b> Seeking Alpha is proud to welcome Symeon Mavroudis as a new contributing analyst. You can become one too! Share your best investment idea by submitting your article for review to our editors. Get published, earn money, and unlock exclusive SA Premium access. </i></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/162255245/image_162255245.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742933-federal-signal-corporation-upward-potential-not-reached-yet", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 08:00:19"}, {"id": "4742930", "title": "BNY Mellon Income Stock Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365758819/image_1365758819.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Financial and business background for Stacking of money coins. Savings and Accounts, Finance Banking Business Concept Ideas, Investments, Funds, Bonds, Dividends and Interest.\" data-id=\"1365758819\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365758819/image_1365758819.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365758819/image_1365758819.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365758819/image_1365758819.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365758819/image_1365758819.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365758819/image_1365758819.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https: