nd medications, pharmaceuticals.\" data-id=\"2166854573\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166854573/image_2166854573.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166854573/image_2166854573.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166854573/image_2166854573.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166854573/image_2166854573.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166854573/image_2166854573.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166854573/image_2166854573.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166854573/image_2166854573.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166854573/image_2166854573.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Buonaventura1955/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The last time I wrote about<strong> Intra-Cellular Therapies</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ITCI\" title=\"Intra-Cellular Therapies, Inc.\">ITCI</a></span>) it was with respect to a Seeking Alpha article entitled \"<strong><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4684055-intra-cellular-more-upside-possible-even-after-positive-mdd-treatment-data\">Intra-Cellular: More Upside Possible Even After Positive MDD Treatment Data</a></strong>\". In</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166854