nd inflation data and potential impact on the pace of expected Fed rate cuts.\u201d</p></blockquote> <h2>Market Review</h2> <p>Municipal bond returns during 3Q24 were buoyed by a solid summer</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1474741936/image_1474741936.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742927-bny-mellon-high-yield-municipal-bond-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 05:47:00"}, {"id": "4742926", "title": "Meta: Potential TikTok Ban Is A Major Catalyst; Upgrade To 'Strong Buy'", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1704413556/image_1704413556.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Social Media Platforms - Facebook, Instagram, YouTube, Pinterest, X, LinkedIn, Reddit, TikTok, Threads\" data-id=\"1704413556\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1704413556/image_1704413556.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1704413556/image_1704413556.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1704413556/image_1704413556.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1704413556/image_1704413556.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1704413556/image_1704413556.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1704413556/image_1704413556.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1704413556/image_1704413556.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1704413556/image_1704413556.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Kenneth Cheung</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4730271-meta-q3-preview-llama-ai-models-could-drive-growth-upgrade-to-buy\">upgraded</a> Meta (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/META\" title=\"Meta Platforms, Inc.\">META</a></span>) (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NEOE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/META:CA\" title=\"Meta Platforms, Inc.\">META:CA</a></span>) to \u2018Buy\u2019 rating in October 2024, highlighting its Llama AI models. On December 6<sup>th</sup>, the appeals court rejected TikTok's bid to overturn a possible US ban</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1704413556/image_1704413556.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742926-meta-potential-tiktok-ban-is-a-major-catalyst-upgrade-to-strong-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 05:08:37"}, {"id": "4742925", "title": "Pakistan On The Comeback Trail - AFC On The Road - Pakistan October 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1483180028/image_1483180028.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Graph growing up in Front Of Pakistan Flag.\" data-id=\"1483180028\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1026px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1483180028/image_1483180028.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1483180028/image_1483180028.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1483180028/image_1483180028.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1483180028/image_1483180028.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1483180028/image_1483180028.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1483180028/image_1483180028.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1483180028/image_1483180028.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1483180028/image_1483180028.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">mirsad sarajlic/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>As part of our on-the-ground research process, Thomas Hugger, CEO of Asia Frontier Capital, visited Karachi and Lahore in Pakistan in October 2024 to meet with the fund\u2019s portfolio companies as well as with policymakers.</em></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1483180028/image_1483180028.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742925-pakistan-on-comeback-trail-afc-on-road-pakistan-october-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 04:59:41"}, {"id": "4742924", "title": "Watts Up With This Stock? The Dividend Power Of NextEra Energy", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183147286/image_2183147286.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Investing in Green Energy: The Financial Power Behind Sustainability\" data-id=\"2183147286\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"878px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183147286/image_2183147286.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183147286/image_2183147286.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280