picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458070413/image_458070413.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Lotus Elise Logo\" data-id=\"458070413\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1012px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458070413/image_458070413.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458070413/image_458070413.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458070413/image_458070413.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458070413/image_458070413.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458070413/image_458070413.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458070413/image_458070413.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458070413/image_458070413.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458070413/image_458070413.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">mchebby</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>We are bearish on Lotus Technology (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LOT\" title=\"Lotus Technology Inc.\">LOT</a></span>) given that we believe the company is facing both macro and micro challenges that will likely put further pressure on the share price.</p> <p>On the macro side, soft consumer demand in China coupled with</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458070413/image_458070413.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742922-lotus-technology-premium-brand-facing-macro-chaos-and-identity-problem", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 04:48:01"}]}